  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我想做一个关于认知系统中「最优握持」（Optimal Grip）的思维导图。这个概念来自具身认知，核心是我们如何在不同尺度上把握信息。根节点就叫「Cognitive/Optimal Grip」吧。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "root((Cognitive<br/Optimal Grip))"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，根节点用双括号表示核心概念。那我先确认一下结构方向——这个「最优握持」下面，您想展开哪些维度？是偏向技术实现还是认知机制？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "root((Cognitive<br/Optimal Grip))"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "两者要结合。我想到十个分支：多尺度感知、关系丰富性、领域转换、情境相关性、涌现追踪、力导向解析、时序排列、交互导航、格式塔感知，还有显著性梯度。每个分支都要体现从认知原理到技术落地的映射。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Multi-scale Perception",
        "Relationship Richness",
        "Domain Transformation",
        "Contextual Relevance",
        "Emergence Tracking",
        "Force Resolution",
        "Temporal Sequencing",
        "Interactive Navigation",
        "Gestalt Perception",
        "Salience Gradients"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，十个一级分支已经添加。我注意到「多尺度感知」这个分支，您想怎么展开？需要体现从微观到宏观的层级吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Multi-scale Perception"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，多尺度感知下面放三个层次：超图层级结构、D3的缩放层级，还有从模式到序列再到类别的认知递进。这三层要体现技术工具如何支撑认知过程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Hypergraph hierarchy",
        "D3 zoom levels",
        "Pattern → Sequence → Category"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到，「关系丰富性」这边我也同步处理——超图的多边关系、Datalog推理、传递依赖，这三项可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Relationship Richness",
        "Hypergraph multi-edges",
        "Datalog inference",
        "Transitive dependencies"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "可以。接下来「领域转换」要强调函数式编程的纯粹性——Haskell纯函数、类型安全组合、占位符替换。这是从认知灵活到代码灵活的关键。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Domain Transformation",
        "Haskell pure functions",
        "Type-safe composition",
        "Placeholder substitution"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "「情境相关性」和「涌现追踪」我有点拿不准优先级。前者侧重Datalog查询和ML打分，后者侧重图分析和聚类——这两个分支的颗粒度需要对齐吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Contextual Relevance",
        "Emergence Tracking",
        "Datalog queries",
        "ML scoring",
        "Graph analysis",
        "ML clustering"
